frames.caption: A chicken stands alert on a forest floor, illuminated by a spotlight in the darkness. The bird's greenish feathers contrast with the dark surroundings, while dry leaves cover the ground.
frames.description: The scene captures a chicken in a forest setting at night. The bird is highlighted by a focused light, creating a stark contrast against the dark, wooded background.

frames.caption: A chicken stands alert on a forest floor covered with dry leaves, illuminated by a bright light. A hand reaches towards the chicken, casting a shadow on the ground.
frames.description: The scene is set in a forest at night, with a chicken standing among fallen leaves. The bright light highlights the chicken and the reaching hand, creating a contrast against the dark background of trees and foliage.
